# .mailmap — canonicalize contributor identities for `git shortlog`,
# `git log --use-mailmap`, and GitHub contributor stats.
#
# Format (pick whichever line form matches the fix you need):
#
#   Proper Name <commit@email.xx>
#   Proper Name <proper@email.xx>                    <commit@email.xx>
#   Proper Name                                      <commit@email.xx>
#   Proper Name <proper@email.xx>   Commit Name      <commit@email.xx>
#
# Lines starting with # are comments.

